VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?:apt-get|yum|apk|dnf)\s+install\s+[^\n]*\bsudo\b
WHEN EXPR MISSING:# intentional|gosu|su-exec|# required
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects installation of sudo or privilege escalation tools inside container images.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for sudo or su Installed in Container.
